*Srce* mi je puno ljubavi za tebe. (My heart is full of love for you.)

Sve što radim, radim iz *srce*. (I do everything from the heart.)

*Srca* su nam sklopila sebe. (Our hearts have connected.)

Voleo bih da čujem tvoje *srce*. (I would love to hear your heart.)

Ona je za mene uvek bio *srce*. (She has always been my heart.)

Imao je živog *srca*. (He had a big heart.)